HEADWORD: prescriptivism
<hw>pre*scrip"tiv*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The doctrine
that acceptable grammatical rules should be prescribed by authority,
rather than be determined by common usage.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>prescriptivist</ent>⟦br⟧
